high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter in front of the toaster.
Open the cabinet under the toaster and take out the container.
Take a step right and walk to the fridge.
Place the container in the fridge and close the door. Wait a moment and take the container out.
Take a few steps left and face the stove.
Put the container on the front right burner of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled container on a stove.

high_descs: Go to the counter to your right, near the toaster.
Open the cabinet in the counter and remove the pan.
Go to the fridge to your right.
Chill the pan in the fridge.
Go to the stove to your left.
Place the pan on the right, front corner of the stove top.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on the stove.

high_descs: turn and walk to the toaster
open cabinet below and get out a pan
turn and walk to the refrigerator
place the pan in the refrigerator and take it back out
turn left and walk to the stove
place the pan on the stove
anns.task_desc: place a cooled pan on the stove
